InventoryActivity

This page can be used for both viewing the user's inventory and also his friends' inventory.
We can search items by search bar and also can specify the search criteria by selecting <....> which shows the exact criteria and user can change that by clicking onto it that creates a pop down menu showing the other criteria.
Clicking onto any item will create a popdown menu that lets user select what to do with that item, eg trade,view details, etc... 
Pressing the down pointing arrow, shows a pop down menu that lets user do things directly related to the user's inventory, like adding an item.

EditProfileActivity

Lets the user edit basic Information.Function for the pop down menu is currently not though of. On the right side we only input text fields

ViewPersonActivity

We can search people/friends by search bar and  <....> shows whether we are looking at list of people or friends and we can change that by clicking it which pops down to show the alternative.
Clicking onto any of the person will create a popdown menu that lets user select what to do with that person, eg trade with,view profile,view his inventory, add him as a friend, delete him from friendlist etc...
